# API Reference menu (SUMMARY.md)

- **Order:** Quickstart → Use the API with AI assistants (MCP) → Reseller → Company → Endpoints.
- **Reseller:** If ≥15 use-cases, use sub-groups: Companies, Users & groups, Training, Phishing simulation, Reports & billing. Max ~8–10 items per group.
- **Company:** Company Admin use-cases go under `api-reference/use-cases/company/` and under a "Company" section in SUMMARY when added.
- **New use-case:** Place under correct role (Reseller vs Company) and correct sub-group; split group if it exceeds 10 items.

Reference: `DOCUMENTATION-RULES.md` (API Reference menu structure).
